node.text:
Made for cuddling.💛 Lucas the llama can’t think of a better way to spend the day than snuggled up to this sweet little one.⁠
⁠
We know how important it is to have a doll that is both safe and cuddly, which is why we’re so proud that ours are safety certified and lovingly handcrafted with natural cotton yarn. All this makes Lucas a wonderful (and very special) gift for little ones.✨⁠
⁠

Fabulous baby flamingos.🦩 If you missed our Baby Animal Collection restock earlier this week, we have good news! Limited quantities of our adorable baby flamingo are still available at the link in our bio.✨⁠
⁠
We can’t get enough of the cute feather tuft on each baby flamingo’s head, and their soft, fuzzy hand-knit wings. It’s these miniature details that have us swooning! Wouldn’t they make the cutest addition to a flamingo-loving little one’s collection? ⁠
⁠
We hope to restock all our baby animals again within the next 2 weeks, so make sure to sign up for back in stock notifications on their product pages, and we’ll send you an email as soon as they’re available again.⁠
⁠
{📸: @ravenvasquezcreative } #babyanimals #babyflamingo #handmadewithlove #1babyanimalequals5meals #cuddleandkind #onemillionmeals #fairtrade

Positively blooming.🌺 Penelope the flamingo is such a fabulous doll for summer, and she would love nothing more than to encourage your little one to embrace their inner confidence. “No one’s better at being you than you. We’re all fabulous in our own way, so let’s act like it!”⁠
⁠
Little ones love to touch and feel Penelope’s special fuzzy wings, and her hand-crocheted flower crown is simply breathtaking.⁠
⁠
If you’ve had your eye on her, she is in stock right now - tap the link in our bio to shop!✨⁠
⁠

If you know a trendy mama or little one, we think Daisy is the perfect match! Tap the link in our bio to see all her details up close.✨⁠

Get a FREE PRINT, today only!🎊 Happy birthday, Hannah the bunny!🎂⁠
⁠
Today, you’ll receive a free print of your choice on orders that include Hannah the bunny! Hurry, offer ends 11:59 pm PST tonight.⁠ Use code HANNAHPRINT
⁠
Hannah the bunny is truly a little work of art. She has so many breathtaking heirloom details, each lovingly handcrafted stitch by beautiful stitch. Our favourite detail is her sweet daisy crown - doesn’t it evoke the dreamiest summer days? And the sweet hand-crocheted scallops on her dress are oh so darling.⁠
⁠
Hannah’s personality is bright and adventurous: “You are my sunshine.”⁠
⁠
Your purchase of Hannah today will provide 10 meals to children in need. Shop now at the link in our bio.✨ Happy birthday, Hannah!⁠
⁠
